What is Class: A class is template
What is Object: Every copy of the class is called its Object
What is relationship b/w class & Object: An object is a copy of class
How class and object are related through syntax:
  ==> NameOfTheClassWhoseCopyYouWantToCreate nameOfTheCopy= new NameOfTheClassWhoseCopyYouWantToCreate();
Memory - Heap and Stack Memory
Visual Representation of Class & Object from memory perspective
